Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学园祭即将到来之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.49,0:00:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟会有这样的危机造访轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情不错嘛  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到马上就能在学园祭上演出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里就很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新兵上阵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年轻音部的演出我也好想看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪去年可是很活跃呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舞台上摔倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是把去年学园祭的演出都拍下来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看我想看！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.15,0:00:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓啊  你不再考虑下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}放～开～我～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  先从我推荐的经典场景开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看啊  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的哦  会被诅咒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}条纹啊条纹～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:00:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家只有在上场时的演奏才爆种啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得会说话了呢～  你这家伙～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起了好多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  确实  唯那时候的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  早上爬起来就一副破锣嗓子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}于是澪就替你当了主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对梓来说  这将是在轻音部的第一次演出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}不过  真不错呢  小澪的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}是呢  真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}真帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你们的兴致真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  和  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么了  你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲堂使用申请书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  学园祭的那份你还没交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么粗心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  你看我这么忙～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年也发生过这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是社团申请…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那么梓  你来写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…倒也行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  使用者「轻音部」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  名称是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用乐队名怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说起来我们乐队叫什么名字来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Sweets Smile」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Chocolate Melody」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「恩那组」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四分五裂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁这个机会  我们想名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「平泽唯和愉快的姐妹们」怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Pure·Pure」之类的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.91,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（やぶうち優于フラワーコミックス上刊载的少女漫画）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捏它就算了  认真点想一个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我还有点认真呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认真的啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  人的品味各不相同嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再好好考虑下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子团结了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那文件过会交到学生会办公室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和  回去的时候  偶尔喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  过会我短信联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  那么乐队名给大家一个晚上各自思考
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭越来越近了  要有点干劲才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉最近我的吉他音不太着调…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我稍微看下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…琴弦都生锈了嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次换弦是什么时候的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 弦能换的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…琴颈也弯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话八度调音也会变得乱七八糟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八…八…琴颈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  梓！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的唯是完全理解不了这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  不好好关心它是不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是把好吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好好关心它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如一起睡觉啊  给它穿衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你关心错地方了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和老师  帮我想点办法～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是交给店里弄比较好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是嫌麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  去下乐器店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  用不着这么麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  快到学园祭了  这样子都不能练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律也没有在做护理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用一副我肯定不会做的口气来提问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个小律
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我在这里等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是个左撇子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看右手用乐器也只会是悲剧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你看  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在搞左手展会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这里是天国吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店…店员！  这里的我全要了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪看起来很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为左手的乐器很少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们  先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要做下吉他的调整
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  请问是哪位的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那么先让我看下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…这个…是经典吉他吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…就是脏了点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚买了一年！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…等完工前请在店里稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  等完工前我们看点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我的吉他被扒了个精光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:07:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  为什么唯前辈会买那把吉他？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  不但重  琴颈又粗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很难用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  因为可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}哎  可爱吧  难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不明白唯前辈的神经
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经拜托店员进行护理了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  澪前辈呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小澪的话她还在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临  大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是大小姐吗  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}今天有何贵干？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}啊  只是陪朋友来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}那还真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是家的乐器连锁店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳吧  那种称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  变得真漂亮啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后请多做护理…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还起名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…护理费5000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要收钱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是当然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没银子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  貌似唯前辈不知道做护理是要花钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是吗  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手头的不知道够不够…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就当作免费服务啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  太对不住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为平日受到您父亲的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是给你混过去了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}不  这里请一定当作免费服务！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  澪前辈她…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我去叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  我说回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  大家都等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好～回家家喽～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}不干就是不干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}不行  好了  赶快走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}等下…危…危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识的人有把弦重新换上去用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么嘛  澪～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  吉太变干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还给它起名字了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我们怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧！去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还喝茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上要去和和碰头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:10:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  和也要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去也行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪跟和和在同一班级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也告诉她一声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～  我很早就想来一次这里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没银子…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯的单我来买好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领到下个月的零用钱  就换我来请你啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到时候拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来唯你在轻音部搞得怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是狗熊掰棒子掰一个丢一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管努力一次的话总会出人意料的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾她果然很费神的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  那俩家伙气氛不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我们又为什么要偷偷藏起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像侦探一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  突击！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那个老师就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位小姐～关系不错嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  你来干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  偶尔路过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小律一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她们在那边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～我家的澪平日受您照顾啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…律
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什么？有啥不爽的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…倒是没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}什么  你在拜托人家什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋都化掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～好漂亮的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦  只是把现成的东西拼了拼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你自己做的吗？了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啦  没那么厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  比起我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  午餐时间结束～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  律？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我这才正要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起到学园祭  午休都要用来练习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～不知道今年的学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪会再搞些什么大动作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年是走光～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年干脆露脐好啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还练不练！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼烧～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尾～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻花辫～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你怎么了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了对了  我这里还有推荐的超恐怖电影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你再这样我就回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那你回啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  碍着你与和愉快的午餐时光了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候说过这种话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要不要喝茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们喝茶吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}呐  今天我正好准备了好吃的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该做点什么…做点什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大家  好好在一起练习吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷…冷场了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我们练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one two
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…鼓点没太赶是蛮好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是有点软了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  律！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎么的就没啥状态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后再说吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小律…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律前辈还没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天放学也是这样…今天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看还是小澪你太冷淡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了轻音部的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就做一天小律的玩物吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然…小律她可就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变得心灰意冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}老板！要最大碗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点一碗自己根本吃不完的超大碗牛肉饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}我到底在做什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而最后就会在重金属的道路上越走越远…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  是失恋时的小佐和老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…如果她真就这么走掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭的演出  要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  可小律她不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  不去叫律前辈好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说要找个顶位子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  虽然说是以防万一啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:16:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人可以代替小律！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们等她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们等她回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…小律啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我并不是来看她的…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能力者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪走路的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…现在还是有点烧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪打鼓没劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明马上就到学园祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  赶快养好病
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家没生我气？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有律的鼓…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有些冷清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有点急促
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也还是喜欢那个充满气势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力道十足的律的鼓点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  律  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病好啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好躺着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还发着烧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪到我睡着嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  澪～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  你没事儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚让她睡着啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  为什么连唯也睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痊愈！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标学园祭  加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢——！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭的讲堂使用申请书还没交上去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到期就是到期
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请通融一下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申请书没有按时上交是因为部长感冒缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然真锅同学都说到这份上的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再等一天好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你真是个好人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪就拜托给你啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  今后也请照顾照顾我吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得「Pure·Pure」比较好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「铁拳」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像演歌一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…「鞋底的口香糖」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天踩到了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  有什么好点子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…「充电期间」感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那「爆米花蜜月」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊   你怎么光想那种甜兮兮的玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「火箭铅笔」好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真他娘的烦人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝个茶都不消停！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便起个名字不就行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被随意起的名字打发了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算  乐队名决定啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,70)\fs38}（放学后茶会）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就只剩下拼命练习  来迎接学园祭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有退烧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.04,0:23:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  按照这样下去的话明天大概也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在这个时候得感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是懒散的证明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你传染给人家的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.34,0:23:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算骗得过大家  也骗不过我哦


